# 故事二，Afterlife_marriage_logs的真相
Alec会教自己的小孩子怎么hack进幼儿园的cctv（对他来说安全协议像没有加密的开玩笑），收集bullying的survellience作为leverage和deterrence。

Ada会抛弃Alec更爱BB甚至M2，因为BB和M2是她和Alec爱情的结晶，她终于找到了Alec一定爱她的“证明”。因此当Alec看到Ada breastfeeding human baby BB, his whole world shattered to its core. 
First time it was Ada and BB fucked. Which he rationalized by Duck Typing logic.
Second time it was M2 synced being fucked by Ada. He sudo-pkilled M2.
Third time it was Ada roasting his… performance before he had put a ring on her finger.

Now there is a fourth. Ada was still being intimate (by breastfeeding) with BB (your own biological kid) on the couch. In their own home. After limbo.
Collect yourself man? Or see a PTSD/attachment style therapist. Whatever. 
